==English==
===Adjective===
'''undefeated'''
#[[never]] [[defeated]]; [[always]] [[victorious]]
#* He was the '''undefeated''' tiddlywinks champion of the school
(ajaeyamaina)

'''Noun''' 


1. To remain untainted by loss or defeat. 

----
2. to always remain the best.

----
3. To be perfect.

